    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the issues surrounding the use of IPv6 site-local unicast addresses in their original form, and formally deprecates them.  This deprecation does not prevent their continued use until a replacement has been standardized and implemented. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
